THAMBI VETTOTHI SUNDARAM SYNOPSIS
Thambi Vettothi Sundaram movie deals with an off-beat subject based on a true story happened in Kanyakumari. It is based on the life of a person in a place that is on the Tamilnadu - Kerala border.

